XACTIVE_MILLER_CLAMP VCC2 GATE_CLAMP VEE2 GND2 TON_COMMAND GATE_MIN_DIG TOFF_COMMAND ONE_EDI3035AS_ACTIVE_MILLER_CLAMP
XOUTPUT_STAGE CURRENT_STATE SOFTOFF VCC2 VEE2 GND2 TON TOFF SASC_CTRL IN_CTRL TON_COMMAND TOFF_COMMAND STP_KEEP_ERROR_DIG 
